<section class="why-guasha reveal">
  <div class="why-guasha-inner">

    <header class="why-guasha-head">
      <p class="why-guasha-eyebrow">Why Gua Sha</p>
      <h2 class="why-guasha-title">What five minutes of pressure<br>actually does.</h2>
    </header>

    <ol class="why-guasha-cols">
      <li class="why-guasha-col">
        <span class="why-guasha-num">01</span>
        <p class="why-guasha-label">Puffiness</p>
        <p class="why-guasha-mech">Sweeping strokes drain the fluid that pools under your eyes overnight.</p>
        <p class="why-guasha-outcome">By 9am, the bloat is gone.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="why-guasha-col">
        <span class="why-guasha-num">02</span>
        <p class="why-guasha-label">Tension</p>
        <p class="why-guasha-mech">Targeted pressure releases the jaw muscle that clenches in your sleep.</p>
        <p class="why-guasha-outcome">Softer profile, fewer headaches.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="why-guasha-col">
        <span class="why-guasha-num">03</span>
        <p class="why-guasha-label">Circulation</p>
        <p class="why-guasha-mech">Five minutes of stone-work multiplies blood flow at the surface.</p>
        <p class="why-guasha-outcome">The flush you'd usually need a long walk to find.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <a href="/blogs/news/gua-sha-statistics-research" class="why-guasha-cite">See the research &rarr;</a>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.why-guasha {
  background: var(--white, #FDFAF5);
  padding: clamp(64px, 9vw, 120px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(30,18,10,0.06);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30,18,10,0.06);
}
.why-guasha-inner {
  max-width: 1180px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Head */
.why-guasha-head {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px);
}
.why-guasha-eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.4em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.why-guasha-title {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3.6vw, 46px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.15;
  letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  color: var(--espresso);
  max-width: 22ch;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Columns */
.why-guasha-cols {
  list-style: none;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: clamp(40px, 5vw, 72px);
  margin: 0 0 clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
  padding: 0;
}
.why-guasha-col {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 14px;
  text-align: left;
}
.why-guasha-num {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(40px, 4vw, 56px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  opacity: 0.32;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}
.why-guasha-label {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--espresso);
}
.why-guasha-mech {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(17px, 1.5vw, 20px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.45;
  color: var(--espresso);
  max-width: 32ch;
}
.why-guasha-outcome {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: var(--stone);
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  max-width: 32ch;
}

/* Citation link */
.why-guasha-cite {
  display: block;
  width: max-content;
  margin: 0 auto;
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  text-decoration: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
  padding: 8px 0;
  transition: color 0.3s var(--ease-premium);
}
.why-guasha-cite:hover {
  color: var(--espresso);
}

/* Mobile */
@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .why-guasha-cols {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .why-guasha-col {
    padding-bottom: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30,18,10,0.08);
  }
  .why-guasha-col:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }
  .why-guasha-num {
    font-size: 36px;
  }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Why Gua Sha",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Why Gua Sha" }]
}
{% endschema %}
